{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 54,
    "name": "سُورَةُ القَمَرِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Qamar",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Moon",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 55,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4847,
        "text": "復活時臨近了，月亮破裂了。",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4848,
        "text": "如果他們看見一種蹟象，他們就退避，而且說：「這是一種有力的魔術。」",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4849,
        "text": "他們否認他，而且順從私欲。每一件事都是確定的。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4850,
        "text": "包含警戒的許多消息，確已來臨他們了，",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4851,
        "text": "那是極精密的智慧；但警告是無效的，",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4852,
        "text": "故你應當避開他們。當召喚者召人於難事的日子，",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 528,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4853,
        "text": "他們不敢仰視地由墳中出來，好像是遍地的蝗蟲；",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4854,
        "text": "大家引頸而奔，群集於召喚者的面前。不信道的人們將說：「這是一個煩難的日子！」",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 211,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4855,
        "text": "在他們之前，努哈的宗族否認過，他們否認過我的僕人，他們說：「這是一個瘋人。」他曾被喝斥，",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4856,
        "text": "故他祈禱他的主說：「我確是被壓迫的，求你相助吧！」",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4857,
        "text": "我就以傾注的雨水開了許多天門，",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4858,
        "text": "我又使大地上的泉源湧出；雨水和泉水，就依既定的狀況而匯合。",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4859,
        "text": "我使他乘坐一隻用木板和釘子製造的船上，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4860,
        "text": "在我的眷顧之下飄流，以報答被人否認者。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4861,
        "text": "我確已將這件事留作一種蹟象，有接受勸告者嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4862,
        "text": "我的刑罰和警告是怎樣的！",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4863,
        "text": "我確已使《古蘭經》易於記誦，有接受勸告的人嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4864,
        "text": "阿德人否認過先知，我的刑罰和警告是怎樣的！",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4865,
        "text": "我確已使暴風在一個很兇惡的日子去毀滅他們，",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4866,
        "text": "暴風將眾人拔起，他們好像被拔出的海棗樹幹一樣。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4867,
        "text": "我的刑罰和警告是怎樣的！",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4868,
        "text": "我確已使《古蘭經》易於記誦，有接受勸告的人嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 463,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4869,
        "text": "賽莫德人否認過警告，",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4870,
        "text": "故他們說：「我們同族的一個凡人，我們能順從他嗎？如果那樣，我們必定陷於迷誤和瘋狂之中。",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4871,
        "text": "難道他們在我們之間獨自奉到啟示嗎？不然，他是說謊者，是傲慢者。」",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4872,
        "text": "他們明日將知道誰是說謊者，誰是傲慢者。",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4873,
        "text": "我必定使母駝考驗他們，故你應當期待他們，並應當堅忍，",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 529,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4874,
        "text": "你應當告訴他們，井水是他們和母駝所均分的，應得水份的，輪流著到井邊來。",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4875,
        "text": "他們曾喊來他們的朋友，他就拿起劍來宰了母駝。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4876,
        "text": "我的刑罰和警告是怎樣的！",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4877,
        "text": "我確以使一種爆炸去毀滅他們，他們就變成造圈欄者所用的枯木。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4878,
        "text": "我確已使《古蘭經》易於記誦，有接受勸告的人嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4879,
        "text": "魯特的宗族曾否認警告，",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4880,
        "text": "我確已使飛沙走石的暴風去毀滅他們；惟魯特的信徒，我在黎明時拯救了他們。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4881,
        "text": "那是從我的主那裡發出的恩典，我如此報酬感謝者。",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4882,
        "text": "他確已將我的懲治警告他們，但他們以懷疑的態度否認警告。",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4883,
        "text": "他們確已誘惑他，叫他不要保護他的客人，但我塗抹了他們的眼睛。你們嘗試我的刑罰和警告吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4884,
        "text": "一種永恆的刑罰在早晨確已襲擊了他們。",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4885,
        "text": "你們嘗試我的刑罰和警告吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4886,
        "text": "我確已使《古蘭經》易於記誦，有接受勸告的人嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 464,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4887,
        "text": "警告確已降臨法老的百姓，",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4888,
        "text": "他們否認了我的一切蹟象，故我以萬能者全能者的態度，懲治了他們。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4889,
        "text": "你們中不信道的人們比這等人還優秀呢？還是天經中有關於你們的赦條呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4890,
        "text": "難道他們說：「我們是一個常勝的團體。」",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4891,
        "text": "那個團體將敗北，他們將轉背。",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4892,
        "text": "不然，復活時是他們的約期；復活時是更艱難的，是更辛苦的。",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4893,
        "text": "犯罪者的確在迷誤和烈火中。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4894,
        "text": "他們匍匐著被拖入火獄之日，將對他們說：「你們嘗試火獄的燒灼吧！」",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4895,
        "text": "我確已依定量而創造萬物，",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 530,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4896,
        "text": "我的命令只是快如轉瞬的一句話。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4897,
        "text": "我確已將你們的宗派毀滅了。有接受勸告的人嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4898,
        "text": "凡他們所做的事，都記載在天經中。",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4899,
        "text": "一切小事和大事，都是被記錄的。",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4900,
        "text": "敬畏的人們，必定在樂園裡，在光明中，",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4901,
        "text": "在全能的主那裡，得居一個如意的地位。",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 531,
        "ruku": 465,
        "hizbQuarter": 212,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
